Notes regarding the GUI:

The Arasan Windows user interface, the source of which is in the "gui"
directory, is also under this license, with the exception of the
"fonts" subdirectory. The fonts, which are loaded at runtime, are
copyrighted, and use of those outside of official Arasan releases will
require a suitable license from the copyright owner(s).

Official binaries of the Arasan Windows GUI installer, which includes
the fonts, may be freely distributed, provided that:

1. It is distributed in unmodified form.
2. No more than a nominal fee is charged for copying or media.

